## Metrics and Monitoring

### Track Coordination Effectiveness

Create `parkboard-worktrees/metrics.sh`:

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Generate coordination metrics

echo "=== COORDINATION METRICS ==="
echo ""

# Active instances
echo "Active Instances: $(grep -l 'State: WORKING' parkboard-worktrees/.scratchpads/*.md | wc -l)"

# Tasks completed today
echo "Tasks Completed Today: $(grep -c "$(date +%Y-%m-%d)" parkboard-worktrees/.coordination/task-board.md || echo 0)"

# Average response time to messages
echo "Open Messages: $(grep -c 'To:.*Priority:' parkboard-worktrees/.scratchpads/*.md)"

# Lock conflicts (same lock requested multiple times)
echo "Lock Conflicts: $(ls parkboard-worktrees/.locks/*.lock 2>/dev/null | wc -l)"

# Commits per instance
echo ""
echo "Commits per instance:"
for worktree in parkboard-worktrees/*/; do
  cd "$worktree"
  instance=$(basename "$worktree")
  commits=$(git log --since="today" --oneline | wc -l)
  echo "  $instance: $commits commits"
done
```

